# 1Password Secrets Template
# This file defines which secrets to fetch from 1Password
# DO NOT put actual secrets here - they will be fetched by scripts/sync-secrets.sh
# 
#   This script will generate a file at $HOME/.secrets 
#   that is then sourced by your .commonrc file
#
# Format: VARIABLE_NAME="op://vault/item/field"
# Example: GITHUB_TOKEN="op://Private/GitHub/token"
#
# To find references:
# - List vaults: op vault list
# - List items: op item list
# - Get item details: op item get "item-name" --format json

# GitLab Access Tokens
